import React from 'react' import { useSelector } from 'react-redux' function ProfileGithub({username}) { const {repos} = useSelector(state=>state.profile); return (

Github Repos

{repos.map(repo => (

{repo.name}

{repo.description}

  • Stars: {repo.stargazers_count}
  • Watchers: {repo.watchers_count}
  • Forks: {repo.forks_count}
))}
) } export default ProfileGithub
